@node "EGS\EGS-Utils\EGS-Eyes.info" "EGS\EGS-Utils\EGS-Eyes.info"

  @{b}@{u}@{fg shine}EGS/EGS-Utils/EGS-Eyes.info@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}

  Icon for the EGS eyes  programm.  This  programm  is  really  rather
  useless.  A  window  will  pop  up which contains 2 eyes that always
  follow the pointer. I dont know if  anybody  use  it  but  I  drawed
  although an icon for it.
@endnode

